snippet.textDisplay: Feedback dite o ajkal bhoi lage, tao dicchi cause I really respect Arnob Da's vision  and the entire Coke Studio Bangla team's for talent. First what was great about the song, composition, lyrics, vocal and arrangement-they were very original and beautiful. What did NOT do justice to the song, the pronunciation of the singers took away from the song and it's clarity. The lyrics were major which got lost in the pronunciation, specially when both the vocals tone & quality were amazing. Hopefully, ei bishoyta ektu apnader bhabnate rakhben in your next composition. Best wishes

snippet.textDisplay: This one feels like a proper back-side track! For the cassette-era kids: when you had 5–6 songs on Side A, you had to flip the cassette to get to Side B. And Side B always needed a ‘filler’ song to make it a full 10. Even the great singers used to drop one like that. This Coke Studio track? Yep, pure Side B energy! 😅🎶

snippet.textDisplay: সবাই প্রশংসাই করবে। আমারও ভীষণ ভালো লাগলো। শুধু গায়কের জন্য একটা কথা যে কিছু অক্ষরের উচ্চারণ স্পষ্ট হলে ভালো হয় যেমন: খ, থ, ভ। দুজনের গায়কীই ভীষণ ভালো।  আশা করি শ্রোতা হিসেবে আমার এই ছোট্ট মন্তব্য বিবেচনায় নেবেন সমালোচনা হিসেবে নয় কিন্তু আরও ভালো করার অভিপ্রায় হিসেবে।
